            "summary": "The new risk assumption notification form can be found [here](https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/policy-statement/2025/july/ps925app9.pdf \"MISPV new risk assumptio",
            "as_at_date": "24/07/2025"
          },
          {
            "rule_number": "6.2",
            "summary": "The group of cells notification form can be found [here](http://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/authorisations/insurance-special-purpose-vehicles/mispv-group-of-cells",
            "as_at_date": "19/01/2019"
          },
          {
            "rule_number": "6.3",
            "summary": "The templates referred to in 5A.6 are the following:",
            "as_at_date": "24/07/2025"
          },
          {
            "rule_number": "6.4",
            "summary": "The instructions referred to in 5A.6 can be found [here](https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-",
